      • get

        public <T> T get(String key,
                 T defaultValue)
        Retrieves a value from SharedPreferences for the specified key. When there is no value associated with the key or the value stored is of a different type than T, then the provided defaultValue will be returned.
        Type Parameters:
        T - type of the return value
        Parameters:
        key - used for storage
        defaultValue - returned in case the key is not found
        Returns:
        when the type matches and a value was stored the value previously stored else the defaultValue.

      • get

        public <T> T get(String key)
        Retrieves a value from SharedPreferences for the specified key. When there is no value associated with the key or the value stored is of a different type than T, then null will be returned.
        Type Parameters:
        T - type of the return value
        Parameters:
        key - used for storage
        Returns:
        when the type matches and a value was stored the value previously stored else null.
